casebody.data:
Helen Kaye MUELLER, Personal Representative of the Estate of Travis Lee Peterson, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
BRANNIGAN BROTHERS RESTAURANTS AND TAVERNS LLC, Austin Smith, Donald Suttle, Jr., Mark McClain, and Shafeek Kanaveh, Defendants-Appellees,
and
API Eden Rock Inc, d/b/a Brannigan Brothers, Defendant. SC: 157771
COA: 335501 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 19, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the April 3, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
